# Changes to CI pipeline require review from the security team.
# This prevents a developer from weakening scan thresholds or removing
# signing steps without an explicit security sign-off.
.github/workflows/          @your-org/security-team

# Policy changes require both security and platform review.
# A policy that's too strict breaks deployments; too loose defeats the purpose.
gitops-config/policies/     @your-org/security-team @your-org/platform-team
gitops-config/argocd/       @your-org/platform-team

# Dockerfile changes require security review — base image, user, capabilities.
app-source/Dockerfile       @your-org/security-team
